# =============================================================================
# BraTS-PEDs Brain Tumour Segmentation — .gitignore
# =============================================================================

# --- Virtual environments ---
# Multiple .venv directories exist due to Python 3.14 compatibility issues
# during setup. Only .venv is active; all are excluded from version control.
.venv/
.venv-1/
.venv-2/
.venv-3/
.venv-4/
venv/
env/

# --- Raw NIfTI dataset ---
# BraTS-PEDs-v1 raw data (NIfTI .nii.gz files, ~tens of GB).
# Download separately from the BraTS challenge portal.
PKG - BraTS-PEDs-v1/

# --- Preprocessed dataset ---
# 39,538 extracted 2D slice pairs (.npy, ~20GB total).
# Regenerate by running notebooks/02_preprocessing.ipynb against the raw NIfTI data.
# Extraction takes ~20 minutes.
processed_dataset/

# --- Model checkpoints ---
# PyTorch .pth files (U-Net 293MB, SegFormer 164MB, FPN ~similar).
# These are large binary files; store separately (e.g. cloud storage, DVC).
checkpoints/
*.pth

# --- Raw array files ---
# NumPy array dumps that may appear outside processed_dataset/ during dev.
*.npy

# --- Markdown docs (keep README.md only) ---
# Internal logbooks/plans/reviews (context.md, current_progress_review.md,
# next_steps_action_plan.md, project_review.md, CLAUDE.md, etc.) stay local.
*.md
!README.md

# --- Python cache ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.pyo

# --- Jupyter checkpoints ---
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- Claude Code local settings (user-specific, not shared) ---
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- OS / editor artifacts ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
